# Scratch / throwaway screenshots
.scratch/
tmp-*.png
audit/corpus_lint/_report.md

# Aegis runtime output (state/reports/capsules are local; ledger lives out-of-worktree)
.aegis/
sessions/
plans/
.taskmaster/state.json
audit/m3-fidelity/

# Throwaway render/debug scripts + bake-off screenshots (session scratch,
# never meant to be committed). Root-anchored PNGs so data/ + app/public
# assets stay tracked. Already-tracked files are unaffected by these.
/*.png
render*.mjs
render_*.mjs
dbg*.mjs
t2x-*.mjs
app/render*.mjs
app/render_*.mjs
app/dbg*.mjs
app/t2x-*.mjs
app/public/figure-check.html
app/public/figure-verify.html

